data.description: Beautifully appointed 5 bedroom home in Spring Hill.  Why build when you can have this less than 2 year young home? This home features an expansive open concept living room and kitchen. The first floor also includes a large office and 1 bathroom.  As you travel upstairs you are greeted with a loft that can be used for a study or additional seating area. The master bedroom has a beautiful ensuite bathroom with separate tub and shower area.  The other 4 bedrooms are located on the opposite side of the loft.  All bedrooms are very spacious with large closets. The back yard is fully fenced with a vinyl fence.  This is truly a wonderful, spacious home.
